    "description": "This course provides a simple conversation Thai language, simple syntax, simple sentences, so that students can simply listening, speaking Thai, but also to recognize some Thai's traditional culture, Thai Food, Thai and the odd tourist classic features.<br>本課程提供簡單的泰文會話、語法及句子的介紹，所以學生們可以聽及說簡單的泰語，而且也能認識泰國的傳統文化、泰國食物、及泰國奇特的旅遊特色。<br>",
